			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value=" Zrell 'greets' the player inside the Tower along with the rest of the Monnrise offencive force during the assault on Moonrise. Nightsong might be alive or dead.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;This is a stand-off - she's protecting the tower, and the players are attacking. Z'rell is confident that she'll put the players and their allies down here, and shows no fear." />
